    "Select how intervals are tuned. Equal Temperament divides the octave into 12 equal steps. Just Intonation uses pure frequency ratios.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wähle die Stimmung für Intervalle. Die gleichstufige Stimmung teilt die Oktave in 12 gleiche Schritte. Reine Stimmung verwendet reine Frequenzverhältnisse."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Select which intervals to practice. At least one must remain active.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wähle die Intervalle aus, die du üben möchtest. Mindestens eines muss aktiv bleiben."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Session best: %@ ¢": {
      "comment": "A label below the current difficulty label, indicating the user's best score for the current difficulty level. The argument is the best score in cents for the current difficulty level.",
